data.eml:eml: A new species of subgenus Neodoryctes Szepligeti (Hymenoptera, Braconidae) from China, with a key to Oriental and Palaearctic species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Li, Tao, Zhang, Ying, van Achterberg, Cornelis (2015): A new species of subgenus Neodoryctes Szepligeti (Hymenoptera, Braconidae) from China, with a key to Oriental and Palaearctic species.
